defaultSince the welfare reform proposals, we’ve worked to ensure our residents are ready. We’ve changed our staffing structures to allow a centralised Income Team and we’ve doubled our Financial Inclusion Team from three to six. 
default&#xa0;
defaultWe’re supporting residents thro
defaultugh face to face visits. We’ve discussed options and completed financial assessments. We also use text messaging for pro-active and missed payments reminders. We use facebook to update our younger customers on welfare reform changes.
