defaultWe’ve also made our staf
defaultf more accessible. Since the welfare reform changes, we’ve added 24 extra contact hours per week for customers to
default speak to an Income Officer or a Lettings Co-ordinator managing a homeless client.
default We can be contacted from 8-8 Monday to Friday and 9-1 on Sat
defaulturdays.
