defaultInternally, we’ve changed our working practices to ensure greater impact. For example, we make time f
defaultor outbound telephone campaigns and carry out visits outside before 9am and after 5pm, as well as Saturday mornings.
default By groups of staff taking to 
defaultthe phones together
default or visits
