defaultWe’ve been working with one LA to provide good quality housing from the private sector to allow them to discharge duty of homeless clients on 12 month assured short hold tenancies. The LA 
defaultsupports
default us financially to manage the tenant, without financial detr
defaultiment to the landlord.
default&#xa0;
defaultFrom year 2 the tenant has received enough support to know how to sustain their tenancy. The LA 
defaultremoves
default financial support and we manage the letting as a private let with the owner. This removes the hassle for the landlord. Removes t
defaulthe problem of failing tenancies and repeated homelessness and provides a stable long term home for a family.
